  "title": "Senior/ Security Officer [Multiple Vacancies, Various Location]",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p><ul><li><p>Conduct screening and checks on all personnel and vehicles entering or exiting the premises.</p></li><li><p>Monitor CCTV systems and observe activities within designated areas.</p></li><li><p>Attend to alarm activations and assess the situation promptly.</p></li><li><p>Respond to incidents such as unattended bags and other security concerns.</p></li><li><p>Patrol and guard the client’s personnel and property.</p></li><li><p>Operate metal detectors, explosive detectors, and X-ray machines at checkpoints.</p></li><li><p>Manage static and access control points.</p></li><li><p>Check passes and other required documents at access points.</p></li><li><p>Issue visitor or contractor passes in exchange for identification cards.</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate records of all incidents.</p></li><li><p>Verify boarding passes, staff passes, and valid entry passes.</p></li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li><p>Minimum GCE 'N' Level qualification</p></li><li><p>Must be able to work on shift hours, weekends and public holidays</p></li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please send in your resume to <a href=\"mailto:gs1@talenttradersg.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com</strong></a>.<br /></p><p>EA License No: 13C6305</p><p>Reg. No.: R24120209 (GAN CHYE SHEN)<br /></p><p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
